        "text": "Alice's Problem: Too Many Rules",
        "emoji": "😫",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "a_intro",
            "text": "There are too many rules in my life!",
            "emoji": "📏",
            "keywords": "too many rules",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "a_morning",
                "text": "In the morning, I have to make my bed and hurry to school.",
                "emoji": "🌅",
                "keywords": "morning, make bed, hurry",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "a3",
                    "text": "Every morning, I have to make my bed before breakfast.",
                    "emoji": "🛏️",
                    "keywords": "make bed, before breakfast",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "a4",
                    "text": "I have to hurry to school because I can't be late for school.",
                    "emoji": "🏃",
                    "keywords": "hurry, late for school",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "a_school",
                "text": "When I'm at school, there are strict rules in class.",
                "emoji": "🏫",
                "keywords": "at school, in class",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "a5",
                    "text": "When I'm at school, I mustn't use my phone in class either.",
                    "emoji": "📵",
                    "keywords": "mustn't use phone",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "a6",
                    "text": "And I have to wear the uniform.",
                    "emoji": "👕",
                    "keywords": "wear uniform",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "a_after",
                "text": "After school, there are even more rules!",
                "emoji": "🎒",
                "keywords": "after school, more rules",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "a8",
                    "text": "I have to finish my homework first.",
                    "emoji": "📝",
                    "keywords": "finish homework first",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "a9",
                    "text": "I can only play basketball after I practise the piano.",
                    "emoji": "🎹",
                    "keywords": "basketball, practise piano",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "a10",
                    "text": "I can't hang out with my friends on weekdays.",
                    "emoji": "🚶",
                    "keywords": "hang out, weekdays",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "a_conclusion",
            "text": "I know some rules are important, but this is awful!",
            "emoji": "😖",
            "keywords": "rules important, awful",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "a12",
                "text": "What can I do?",
                "emoji": "❓",
                "keywords": "What can I do",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "dr_know",
        "text": "Dr Know's Advice: Rules Build Character",
        "emoji": "👨‍⚕️",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "d_intro",
            "text": "Rules can help you to become a better person.",
            "emoji": "🌟",
            "keywords": "better person",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "d_logic",
                "text": "Every rule has a good reason behind it.",
                "emoji": "💡",
                "keywords": "good reason",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "d3",
                    "text": "You mustn't be late for class because it shows respect for your class and teacher.",
                    "emoji": "🤝",
                    "keywords": "not late, respect",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "d5",
                    "text": "You can't use your phone in class because you need to focus on learning.",
                    "emoji": "📵",
                    "keywords": "no phone, focus",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "d6",
                    "text": "You have to wear a uniform because it builds school spirit.",
                    "emoji": "🏅",
                    "keywords": "uniform, school spirit",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "d_positive",
                "text": "Think about the things you can do!",
                "emoji": "🌈",
                "keywords": "things you can do",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "d8",
                    "text": "You can use your phone at home.",
                    "emoji": "🏠",
                    "keywords": "phone at home",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "d9",
                    "text": "You can relax after you finish your homework.",
                    "emoji": "🏖️",
                    "keywords": "relax, after homework",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "d10",
                    "text": "And you can hang out with friends at weekends!",
                    "emoji": "🚶",
                    "keywords": "hang out, weekends",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "d_conclusion",
            "text": "Remember: No rules, no order!",
            "emoji": "📜",
            "keywords": "No rules, no order",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
